data.description: This wonderful 5 bed 2 bath homes sits on a nice private lot and has so much to offer! Spacious kitchen with new flooring, backsplash and lighting. Hardwood floors in living room and main floor bedrooms. Full bath with skylight, jet tub and new wl floor. Quality Pella thermopane windows. Lower level family room with surround sound, 2 bedrooms, full bath, large utility and storage room with access to fully fenced backyard, 2 car garage and dbl door shed. Whole house fan. American standard high efficiency furnace 2017-cac and hwh 3 to 4 years old, new water softener. Security camera, monitor and netted gazebo stay.  Easy access to all major expressways shopping and dining.
